	<Title>
		Pap smear: Still needed after hysterectomy?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Many women who&apos;ve had hysterectomies no longer need routine Pap smears.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Are Pap smears still needed after removal of the uterus (hysterectomy)?
	</Question>
